name: Rang-Da
description:
In traditional Balinese folktale, Rang-Da is the demon queen who leads the forces of evil to destroy forces of good. The mythology also describe, Rang-Da is a child-eating ghost and hunts women. For your information, the rendition of Rang-Da in this piece is purely my imagination. There is no intention to insult any Balinese or Hinduism. Thank you.

This is a #HENHALLOWEEN special edition.
